{"tid":1782594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"17 歲女學生藏𠝹刀被控　續獲保釋候訊","createTime":"2019-12-14T05:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T02:03:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7bcc62ae682c7674601ee292c7fd234c1f9159","tid":1782594,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:56:17.000Z","msg":"今年11月中旬，有網民發起全港三罷行動，多區發生衝突，當中17歲中六女學生被指管有一把𠝹刀，而被控一項管有攻擊性武器罪，案件今於東區裁判法院再提堂，被告身穿校服到庭應訊，控方指仍需時索取相關的閉路電視片段，及向律政司索取法律意見，申請押後案件至明年1月10日再訊，獲裁判批准，期間被告獲准繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被告馬麗雅（學生，17歲），被控一項管有攻擊性武器罪，指她今年11月11日，銅鑼灣怡和街9至15號後巷管有一把𠝹刀。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/17-%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%97%8F%F0%A0%9D%B9%E5%88%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7-%E7%BA%8C%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F17-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2597%258F%25F0%25A0%259D%25B9%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=bd6e99fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F17-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2597%258F%25F0%25A0%259D%25B9%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&h=f2240a85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/17-%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%97%8F%F0%A0%9D%B9%E5%88%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7-%E7%BA%8C%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A/</a>"},{"pid":"f988883a9d4f33df60a8fb77408d717d1a575a89","tid":1782594,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:56:38.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link targe